292
00:22:54,060 --> 00:22:55,150
I need your help.

293
00:22:56,360 --> 00:22:57,030
Help?

294
00:22:58,400 --> 00:23:00,240
Because you're not the one being trained today,

295
00:23:01,130 --> 00:23:02,030
but me.

296
00:23:07,340 --> 00:23:09,010
One, two.

297
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:20,380
Mr. Tu, hold on.

298
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:21,640
Here, it's

299
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:24,760
one, two, three, four.

300
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:25,770
Okay?

301
00:23:25,790 --> 00:23:26,730
One more time.

302
00:23:35,750 --> 00:23:36,780
Youning, are you okay?

303
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:37,730
I'm fine.

304
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,210
Tu Jinghe,

305
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,710
