323
00:25:09,570 --> 00:25:10,540
Zhang Yiqing, right?

324
00:25:11,210 --> 00:25:13,380
I think he's quite interested in you.

325
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,300
There was a misunderstanding between us,

326
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:18,000
but now it's resolved.

327
00:25:18,250 --> 00:25:21,070
So... I'm half a matchmaker?

328
00:25:24,930 --> 00:25:25,700
I'm sorry.

329
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,050
You don't have to apologize.

330
00:25:28,050 --> 00:25:29,130
We don't owe each other anything.

331
00:25:30,010 --> 00:25:31,880
No, I broke off the engagement.

332
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,040
I should be responsible.

333
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:35,950
If you want to take responsibility, then take it till the end.

334
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:37,020
Even if it's just an act,

335
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:37,850
finish it up.

336
00:25:37,870 --> 00:25:38,710
What are you talking about?

337
00:25:38,830 --> 00:25:39,590
I just want to tell you

338
00:25:39,590 --> 00:25:40,730
I can't continue acting.

339
00:25:40,730 --> 00:25:41,880
If you break off the engagement now,

340
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:42,870
I'll tell my dad.

341
00:25:43,490 --> 00:25:44,650
My dad listens to me.

342
00:25:44,670 --> 00:25:45,740
If I complain to him

343
00:25:45,770 --> 00:25:46,640
your company will be over.

344
00:25:46,660 --> 00:25:47,820
Zhou Youning, are you crazy?

345
00:25:47,850 --> 00:25:48,700
I already told you

346
00:25:48,700 --> 00:25:49,900
