347
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:51,090
Why do I have to go all the way in this act?

348
00:25:53,990 --> 00:25:55,740
You can keep acting, right?

349
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:05,710
Why are we here again?

350
00:26:06,990 --> 00:26:08,550
Since that accident,

351
00:26:09,150 --> 00:26:10,860
I haven't eaten here again.

352
00:26:12,090 --> 00:26:13,750
I even avoided the area

353
00:26:14,150 --> 00:26:15,320
near this restaurant.

354
00:26:15,750 --> 00:26:17,020
Don't force yourself.

355
00:26:20,990 --> 00:26:22,750
I'm being trained today.

356
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,270
I hope you can help me

357
00:26:25,270 --> 00:26:26,640
celebrate my birthday this year.
